definitions.definition: The largest member of the deer family ( Alces americanus , sometimes included in Alces alces ), of which the male has very large, palmate antlers .
examples: We saw a moose at the edge of the woods.

definitions.definition: Any of the extinct moose-like deer of the genera Cervalces and Libralces .
( figuratively , derogatory , colloquial ) An ugly person.
